<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><em>Then suddenly my heart is wrung<br />
By her distracted air<br />
And I remember wildness lost<br />
And after, swept from there,<br />
Am set down standing in the wood<br />
At the death of the hare.</em><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span> — Yeats</p>
</div>
<p>This hare did not die. This hare is not a victim.</p>
<p>Based on the lore established in <a href="/scp-001-o5">SCP-001:O5</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adminbright" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(224440); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=224440&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561789020" alt="AdminBright" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=224440)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adminbright" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(224440); return false;">AdminBright</a></span>.<br />
Also partly inspired by a line in <a href="/scp-1764">SCP-1764</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drclef" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(213153); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=213153&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1561789020" alt="DrClef" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=213153)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drclef" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(213153); return false;">DrClef</a></span>.</p>
<p>I've always felt like &quot;that one time the Foundation committed genocide&quot; deserved to be revisited, so here we are.</p>
<p>Thank you for reading.</p>
